  "instructions": [
    "In a food processor, pulse the cashews until coarsely chopped.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together the flour, Parmesan cheese, egg, melted butter, parsley, salt, pepper, and baking powder.",
    "Stir in the chopped cashews until they are evenly coated with the batter.",
    "Using a spoon, drop the cashew mixture into balls, about 1 1/2 inches in diameter.",
    "Heat the air fryer to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Place the cashew balls in a single layer in the air fryer basket.",
    "Cook for 5-7 minutes or until golden brown, shaking the basket halfway through.",
    "Serve warm and enjoy!"
